### Note on ideas vs. text · 關於「概念」與「文字」的說明

Copyright protects the **expression** (this text), not the **ideas** of the
framework. The concepts of Genesis — its layers, engine, principles, and
boundaries — are free for anyone to think with, teach, critique, and extend.
This license governs only the wording of these documents and asks, in return,
only for attribution.

著作權保護的是**表達**（本文字），而非框架的**概念**。Genesis 的概念——其層級、
引擎、準則與邊界——任何人皆可自由援引、教學、批評與延伸。本授權僅規範這些文件的
文字表述，所求者唯「標示出處」而已。

